task.summary:
Reorded some stuff for easier stack method writing
also, switched char type for uint8_t in message struct to avoid file problems
Added File Stack Methods, skeleton for card_task

Refactored Code
Moved tasks to can_collector_utils.c
Added Elm327 init function and defs for selecting UART
Added GPS parsing and modified RX task for GPS addition
Changed SIM pins & disabled debug output
Stack now deletes partial messages to conserve stack integrity
Fixed data parsing from GPS v2
Fixed Compile errors & added VIN confirmation
Fix in case of corrupted stack file
